To return to normal size, disable code and switch gear.
Replace X's with desired size.
3F800000 = Normal Size
40000000 = 2x as big
40400000 = 3x as big
40800000 = 4x as big
41000000 = 8x as big


Swords/Spears:

30000000 101C1D40
10000000 50000000
31000000 00002580
30100000 00000000
10000000 50000000
31000000 00000B24
30100000 00000000
10000000 50000000
31000000 00000040
